## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in the field of gender equality. Additionally, the data is limited to the sources accessed, which may not fully represent the global context. Further research and updated data are necessary to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the current state of gender barriers.